---
title: Brie, Caramelized Onion and Steak Sandwiches with Apple Arugula Salad and Fig Vinaigrette
description: Fig jam and caramelized onions come together with ooey-gooey melted brie in this irresistible sandwich. The sweet richness is balanced by a zesty apple and arugula salad on the side.
